      "role": "user",
      "content": "it sounds nice in theory but it doesn't feel real. i'm thousands of miles from anyone who actually knows me. if i didn't text my mom for a week she'd probably just think i'm busy working. it's like i'm just taking up space in a city that doesn't care if i'm here or not. it feels less like \"contributing to a story\" and more like i'm just a glitch in the system that no one is trying to fix.",
